      "review_summary": "The PR changes Telegram generic and native slash-command handling so authorized control commands get command metadata and native status-notice replies are resolved and delivered directly, with command reply metadata and regression tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +129, Tests +284. Total +413 across 16 files.\n\nReproducibility: Source-reproducible for the patch regression: the PR head calls `getReplyFromConfig` before the dispatcher, while current dispatcher code is where resolver delivery mode and progress callbacks are injected. I did not run a live Telegram repro in this read-only review.",
